---
title: Middle Eastern Cauliflower & Almond Couscous with Plant-Based Mayo
description: It’s our favourite fluffy veggie, this time roasted in Middle Eastern spices so that the flavour pops out of the Israeli couscous when it’s stirred through with the other veggies and roasted almonds. Oh it’s cauliflower by the way, we’re talking about cauliflower, we can’t get enough of it!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
